@host = https://localhost:7001
@materialUnitId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Database summary
GET {{host}}/dev/database-summary

### Pick a real material first, then copy the id into @materialUnitId
GET {{host}}/dev/material-sample?take=10

### Feature vector
GET {{host}}/analytics/features/{{materialUnitId}}

### Calculate and store risk score
POST {{host}}/risk-scores/materials/{{materialUnitId}}/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riskType": "OverallQualityRisk",
  "modelVersion": "rule-risk-v1.0",
  "storeResult": true
}

### Calculate risk for recent materials
POST {{host}}/risk-scores/calculate-all
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "siteId": null,
  "riskType": "OverallQualityRisk",
  "maxMaterials": 50,
  "storeResult": true
}

### Risk models
GET {{host}}/risk-scores/models?activeOnly=true

### Dashboards
GET {{host}}/analytics/dashboard/overview

### Quality dashboard
GET {{host}}/analytics/dashboard/quality

### Risk dashboard
GET {{host}}/analytics/dashboard/risk?highRiskTake=20

### Data-quality dashboard
GET {{host}}/analytics/dashboard/data-quality

### Report JSON
GET {{host}}/reports/materials/{{materialUnitId}}/investigation

### Report PDF
GET {{host}}/reports/materials/{{materialUnitId}}/investigation/pdf
